00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:30.449
more junk food be one of the fastest ways
to gain weight?

00:00:30.449 --> 00:00:35.370
Eating a diet of burgers, fried chicken and
french fries. Wouldn't that put on weight

00:00:35.370 --> 00:00:39.420
quickly?
Well there's a good reason why you want to

00:00:39.420 --> 00:00:42.430
take a different approach.
Although it seems like stuffing yourself with

00:00:42.430 --> 00:00:46.730
junk food might be one of the speediest ways
to gain weight, you need to realize that this

00:00:46.730 --> 00:00:50.530
kind of food is often very HIGH in saturated
fat.

00:00:50.530 --> 00:00:54.320
