in the form of lean muscle mass, that is distributed

00:01:21.060 --> 00:01:25.950
throughout your body - that makes you look
stronger, fitter, and more attractive.

00:01:25.950 --> 00:01:32.300
So, at the top of the list of 'Foods to Avoid'
and stay away from is: Fried Foods, and foods

00:01:32.300 --> 00:01:36.880
loaded in saturated fat.
This means staying away from high fat, processed

00:01:36.880 --> 00:01:43.000
meats like salami. Staying away from ice cream
and most frozen desserts as well.

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:49.409
And then next, you want to avoid empty calorie
foods that contain little or no nutritional

00:01:49.409 --> 00:01:52.200
value.
And the biggest culprit of this is 'Refined

00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:57.509
Sugars' like sweets and candy bars.
Just remember, gaining weight healthily involves

00:01:57.509 --> 00:02:02.619
eating more calories, so that you have enough
fuel in your body to support and encourage

00:02:02.619 --> 00:02:06.520
a weight gain and increase in your overall
muscle mass.

00:02:06.520 --> 00:02:11.150
And if you're skinny, and not used to eating
these amounts of foods, you need to train

00:02:11.150 --> 00:02:14.569
yourself to increase your appetite.
And if you're finding it a challenge to eat

00:02:14.569 --> 00:02:20.629
all the calories you need, you need to make
sure that every single mouthful you take is

00:02:20.629 --> 00:02:25.400
packed full of healthy, nutritious food, that
will serve your body well, and help you gain

00:02:25.400 --> 00:02:29.510
healthy weight.
So, avoid most sugary food, except for the

00:02:29.510 --> 00:02:34.640
