well - or sugar alternatives - because they're

00:02:44.620 --> 00:02:52.230
way too high in sugar.
'Number 3' to avoid is: Avoid 'empty calorie'

00:02:52.230 --> 00:02:57.150
foods such as white flour products, because
your body treats these in a similar way to

00:02:57.150 --> 00:02:59.940
sugar.
So instead of white bread, choose wholemeal

00:02:59.940 --> 00:03:05.930
bread. And instead of normal pasta, go for
whole wheat pasta.

00:03:05.930 --> 00:03:09.560
And then finally, you want to minimize your
consumption of alcohol as well, if your aim

00:03:09.560 --> 00:03:14.239
is to gain healthy weight. Again, alcoholic
drinks tend to be loaded with empty calories.

00:03:14.239 --> 00:03:18.560
And alcohol actually has a 'catabolic' - a
destructive effect - on muscle. Meaning it

00:03:18.560 --> 00:03:24.510
